---
title: One-Pot Moroccan Pork & Veggie Pilaf Rice with Yoghurt & Roasted Cashews
description: One pot cooking isn’t just convenient, it’s also full of lots of lovely flavours as everything comes together. Take a pork and veggie pilaf, the Moroccan and chermoula spices melt in the bowl. One irresistible and easy dinner coming right up!

*This recipe is under 550kcal per serving.*
